\u00e5r Marit Oliva Hammervik fridykker, finner hun roen hun s\u00e5 sjelden opplever i hverdagen."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article6652281.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/fridykk4.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/9164ef345947b5d19788269dbad2dc75aa8a954e.jpg?597825f8"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Finner roen med fridykking -adressa.no", "Hel\u00e5rssport", "En sport for alle", "Godt alternativ"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "9164ef345947b5d19788269dbad2dc75aa8a954e"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim", "ukeadressa", "eadressa", "skattelister", "d\u00f8dsfall", "tr\u00f8nder", "trafikk"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "nyheter,trondheim,ukeadressa,eadressa,skattelister,d\u00f8dsfall,tr\u00f8nder,trafikk"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["sport", "sprek"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "family-and-parenting"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["fridykking", "finner roen"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["manger", "d. en", "b\u00f8rje m\u00f8ster", "manger og toska", "frivannsliv", "norsk undervannsintervensjon"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["fr\u00f8ya", "norge", "hordaland"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["jan risberg", "marit oliva hammervik", "frode trefall"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["sport", "sport/sprek"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article6652281.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/fridykk4.jpg"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": "adressa.no"}, {"field": "og-title", "value": "Finner roen med fridykking"}, {"field": "og-type", "value": "article"}, {"field": "og-url", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/sport/sprek/article6652227.ece"}, {"field": "p